				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Nimble is in moonrise towers, preparing to leave for the city. In the top set of nodes wulbren is dead, and she is feeling lost and sad. In the bottom, wulbren is alive (nickels is dead) and she is doing her best to get organised, while fighting her grief over the loss of her friend."
